- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the generation of follow-up test cases and the tool used for metamorphic testing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the impact of source test case generation techniques on fault detection effectiveness. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of weak mutation and random test generation strategies for source test case generation, which are commonly used in machine learning testing.
